  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_antiretroviral_therapy_drug__snomed_ct_dm_d_">ANTIRETROVIRAL THERAPY DRUG (SNOMED CT DM+D)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_clinical_terminology_code">CLINICAL TERMINOLOGY CODE</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_antiretroviral_therapy_drug__snomed_ct_dm_d_">ANTIRETROVIRAL THERAPY DRUG (SNOMED CT DM+D)</xref>
 is the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_snomed_ct">SNOMED CT</xref>
® concept ID from the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_nhs_dictionary_of_medicines_and_devices">NHS Dictionary of Medicines and Devices</xref>
 which is used to identify the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_antiretroviral_therapy">Antiretroviral Therapy</xref>
 drug prescribed to a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 at the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_hiv_clinic_attendance">HIV Clinic Attendance</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="supportingInformation" keyref="supporting_definition_snomed_ct_refset">SNOMED CT Refset</xref>
 Metadata:        </p>
